  <Summary>Kate summons Klaus, using a gift he gave her 50 years before, and begs him to save her children and grandchildren.  He finds them trapped in Xmasville, where he had fought the Partridge family and the Pola-Cola Corporation many years before.  Attempting to acquire and pervert Christmas, the Partridges are selling children to aliens.  After a lengthy battle Klaus defeats the villains and frees the children.  Years later he visits Kate's now-grown granddaughter, and gives her the gift he had once given the now-deceased Kate.</Summary>
